### List tasks
GET http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks

### Create a task
POST http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries",
  "description": "Milk, eggs, bread"
}

### Create another task
POST http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Write tests"
}

### Get task by ID
GET http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks/task_1

### Update task (mark as done)
PATCH http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks/task_1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": true
}

### Update task title
PATCH http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks/task_1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy organic groceries"
}

### Delete a task
DELETE http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks/task_1

### Get deleted task (→ 404)
GET http://localhost:7331/api/v1/tasks/task_1

### Health check
GET http://localhost:7331/health
